summary: An ordinance approving amended assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1328, for the improvement of Wallingford Avenue, from North to Woodlawn Avenue; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle by grading and curbing the same, under Ordinance No. 14974 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
